OL,3,CStudent, 70, graduates despite sight
OL,4,Closs trauma
OL,6,FA 70-year-old grandfather who left
OL,7,Fschool with four O-Levels has
OL,8,Fgraduated from university despite
OL,9,Flosing most of his eyesight during his
OL,10,Fdegree.
OL,12,FPaul Deal was half way through his
OL,13,Fmaster's (MA) in history when his
OL,14,Fvision began to blur while he was
OL,15,Fwalking the dog.
OL,17,FThinking nothing of it, he considered
OL,18,Fringing an optician for advice.
