OL,3,CStudent, 70, graduates despite sight
OL,4,Closs trauma
OL,6,FBut at 2am the next day, Mr Deal was
OL,7,Frushed into theatre, where an eye
OL,8,Fsurgeon sought to halt an infection
OL,9,Fthat was rapidly travelling through
OL,10,Fhis right eye.
OL,12,FMr Deal, who had spent 40 years as a
OL,13,Fjournalist, said: "It was a traumatic
OL,14,Ftime. After another operation the next
OL,15,Fday I was told I might not get my
OL,16,Fsight back. I thought 'what the hell
OL,17,Fam I going to do about my MA now?'"
OL,19,FMr Deal was left with around 20%
OL,20,Fvision in his right eye and not much
OL,21,Fmore in his left.
