OL,6,FHe deferred his history MA by a year
OL,7,Fas he made frequent visits to Bristol
OL,8,FEye Hospital and investigated
OL,9,Fassistive technology to aid reading,
OL,10,Fafter struggling with a magnifying
OL,11,Flens.
OL,13,FThe father-of-three returned to his
OL,14,Fstudies, only to suffer a spate of
OL,15,Fnose bleeds so severe that he ended up
OL,16,Fin A&E three times.
OL,18,FLaser eye surgery on his left eye
OL,19,Freturned some of his sight.
