OL,3,CStudent, 70, graduates despite sight
OL,4,Closs trauma
OL,6,FStill unable to drive, Mr Deal would
OL,7,Ftake two trains and a bus to get to
OL,8,Fthe university in Bristol from his
OL,9,Fhome near Bradford-on-Avon.
OL,11,FDespite this, he struggled on and
OL,12,Ffinished his mammoth 15,000 word
OL,13,Fdissertation.
OL,15,F"I'd always loved the idea of going
OL,16,Fback to education," added Mr Deal.
