OL,3,CStudent, 70, graduates despite sight
OL,4,Closs trauma
OL,6,F"Growing up in east London and Essex I
OL,7,Fnever thought I'd go to university.
OL,8,FNever. None of my family had gone and
OL,9,FI was just completely focused on
OL,10,Fbecoming a journalist."
OL,12,FHe graduated in front of his wife,
OL,13,FDiana and youngest daughter, Rebecca.
OL,15,F"It's been a heck of a time and I'm
OL,16,Fvery proud to be graduating. I've been
OL,17,Flooking forward to this day
OL,18,Fimmensely," he added.
