OL,3,CStudent, 70, graduates despite sight
OL,4,Closs trauma
OL,6,F"I wondered how I'd cope at university
OL,7,Fand it was hard at times. However, I
OL,8,Flearnt that, even at prestigious
OL,9,Finstitutions like Bristol, you are
OL,10,Fmade welcome by students and teachers,
OL,11,Fno matter if you are older.
OL,13,F"I also feel very positively towards
OL,14,Fthe university for supporting me
OL,15,Fthrough the difficult times.
OL,17,F"I would love to think that someone
OL,18,Fwho's stopped working might see my
OL,19,Fstory and consider becoming a student.
