OL,6,F"I miss studying here and I made some
OL,7,Fgood friends along the way."
OL,9,FWhile studying for A-Levels `
OL,10,Fincluding one in history ` Mr Deal got
OL,11,Fa summer job as an editorial messenger
OL,12,Fboy on the Basildon-based Evening Echo.
OL,14,FSpotting a big story that the newsroom
OL,15,Fhad overlooked got him noticed by the
OL,16,Feditor, who offered him a position as
OL,17,Ftheir first trainee reporter.
