OL,6,FDuring his career he reported briefly
OL,7,Ffrom Northern Ireland and edited
OL,8,Fnewspapers including the Bath Evening
OL,9,FChronicle and the Northamptonshire
OL,10,FEvening Telegraph.
OL,12,FHe spent 15 years at the BBC,
OL,13,Fproducing national news bulletins, and
OL,14,Flater worked as a communications
OL,15,Fofficer for Wiltshire Police.
OL,17,FAfter retirement he enrolled on a
OL,18,FUniversity of Bristol history short
OL,19,Fcourse, which aimed to help mature
OL,20,Fstudents progress to a full degree.
